  "name": "Family Tree",
  "description": "A full-stack family tree and legacy platform for building, visualizing, and managing generational family history, rendering interactive hierarchical trees with React Flow and Dagre atop a normalized PostgreSQL backend. It includes role-based collaboration, member profiles with linked memory timelines, GEDCOM import, and optional AI-assisted biography generation.",
